    README for distribution

- prepare source archive (in main directory of checked out archive):
    dev/pack 0.6

- tag current commit:
    git tag v0.6

- prepare precompiled binaries (in checked out or unpacked archive):
    # galaxy
    make bin86 ARCH=i686 ALSANC=~/stereo/bitbucket/alsa/
    # beteigeuze
    make bin86 ARCH=x86_64 ALSANC=~/stereo/bitbucket/alsa/
    # musik
    make bin86 ARCH=ARIAG25 ALSANC=/root/alsa/
    # pi
    make binPi ARCH=RaspberryPi ALSANC=/root/alsa/

- copy archives to web repository and adjust description/links


